    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >服务业末日之旅</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Roman Sands RE:Build》由创作出 IGF 得奖之作《Paratopic》的工作室打造而成，欢迎各位玩家一探究竟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豪华热带度假村与末日生存之地不停切换，交织出了一部荒诞的幻想冒险故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >双故事线，逃出生天</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231460/extras/4bdc3323839d7e4cfc59e914e5345cdf.poster.avif?t=1756159381\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231460/extras/4bdc3323839d7e4cfc59e914e5345cdf.webm?t=1756159381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231460/extras/4bdc3323839d7e4cfc59e914e5345cdf.mp4?t=1756159381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >度假村</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海浪将主角冲到奢华度假村的沙滩上。据客人们所示，你是这个度假村的员工。没时间偷懒了，玩家必须尽快升级、赚取装备，应对客人们无止境的要求。更要命的是，太阳即将吞噬整个世界，但客人们却毫不在意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入体验故事剧情：破解谜题，揭开度假村的秘密，找到逃出这个世界的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >末日将至，拼命求生</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231460/extras/d6db57a1aa5bb2ca78ba3e0042e8c403.poster.avif?t=1756159381\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231460/extras/d6db57a1aa5bb2ca78ba3e0042e8c403.webm?t=1756159381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231460/extras/d6db57a1aa5bb2ca78ba3e0042e8c403.mp4?t=1756159381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >研究设施</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家是其中一名幸存者，负责管理一座破旧的动物研究设施。身边只有一头死牛，以及收音机里传来的声音；这声音很熟悉，但...声音的主人究竟在哪里？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有东西干扰设施运作，你会不惜一切代价消灭它吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >疯狂的双重世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这两个世界是同一个世界吗？时间先后顺序为何？两者究竟有着怎么样的关联！ ？在这部疯狂的末日题材游戏中，玩家能体验到两种截然不同的叙事风格，尽情享受这个由冒险、视觉小说、解谜、生存模拟和恐怖氛围等元素所交织出的末日困境吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231460/extras/6645c72cc9e76a07225190d81a4035bc.poster.avif?t=1756159381\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231460/extras/6645c72cc9e76a07225190d81a4035bc.webm?t=1756159381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231460/extras/6645c72cc9e76a07225190d81a4035bc.mp4?t=1756159381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
